HEADWORD: Eikonogen
<hw>Ei*kon"o*gen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>e'ikw`n</grk>, <grk>e'iko`nos</grk>, image + root of
